OL,3,CAerosmith announces retirement from
OL,4,Ctouring after Steven Tyler vocal injury
OL,6,FAerosmith have announced their
OL,7,Fretirement from the touring stage as
OL,8,Ffrontman Steven Tyler's injured voice
OL,9,F"is not possible" to recover fully.
OL,11,FThe US rock band, known for hits
OL,12,Fincluding Dream On, Dude (Looks Like A
OL,13,FLady) and Walk This Way, cancelled
OL,14,Fdates on their farewell tour last
OL,15,FSeptember due to Tyler needing
OL,16,F"ongoing care" for damage to his vocal
OL,17,Fcords and a fractured larynx.
OL,19,F"As you know, Steven's voice is an
OL,20,Finstrument like no other," the band
OL,21,Fsaid in a statement on X.
