OL,3,CAerosmith announces retirement from
OL,4,Ctouring after Steven Tyler vocal injury
OL,6,F"He has spent months tirelessly
OL,7,Fworking on getting his voice to where
OL,8,Fit was before his injury. We've seen
OL,9,Fhim struggling despite having the best
OL,10,Fmedical team by his side.
OL,12,F"Sadly, it is clear, that a full
OL,13,Frecovery from his vocal injury is not
OL,14,Fpossible.
OL,16,F"We have made a heartbreaking and
OL,17,Fdifficult, but necessary, decision `
OL,18,Fas a band of brothers ` to retire from
OL,19,Fthe touring stage."
