OL,6,FLast year, the band said that Tyler's
OL,7,Fvocal injury was "more serious than
OL,8,Finitially thought" as they cancelled
OL,9,Ftour dates.
OL,11,FThe group, which includes Joe Perry,
OL,12,FTom Hamilton, Joey Kramer and Brad
OL,13,FWhitford, said it has been "the honour
OL,14,Fof our lives to have our music become
OL,15,Fpart of yours".
OL,17,F"It was 1970 when a spark of
OL,18,Finspiration became Aerosmith," the
OL,19,Fstatement said.
